							Well it seems every time I've put some time aside to update
					the page a bit Innoruuk.com has been unavailable for one reason
					or another. Hopefully things will start cooperating and I can
					get some stuff done.<br><br>
					Tonight is our meeting as well. I'm getting the agenda together as
					we speak. Hope to see you all there as this is our first official
					meeting as a guild.
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com">Boisvert</a><br><br>
