						<font face="verdana" color="#6B5A39" size="-2">
						Saturday, January&nbsp;13
					</td>
				<tr>
					<td colspan="2">
						<font face="verdana" color="#BFBFBF" size="-1">
						<div align="justify">
							This weekend we had a raid double header! On Saturday to the Efreeti
					where we picked up 6 pairs of his shiney little boots and one of
					his rings. On Sunday it was off to Kedge where we fought down to
					Phin's room although he had not yet spawned and picked up a swirlspine belt!
					Sadly we were forced to evac when someone thought they could pull
					better than the monk!
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com">Boisvert</a><br><br>
							<center><hr size="1" color="#6B5A39" width="200"><center>
