					<td colspan="2">
						<font face="verdana" color="#BFBFBF" size="-1">
						<div align="justify">
							Since Starkan doesn't seem to be getting any HTML done I'm going to start
					working through that. Also, with the coming changes to Innoruuk.com
					we might not be able to host our page so keep your eye for that.
					Once things do finalize out a bit we'll start getting news updating
					access to the Council members so I wont be the only one updating.
					<br><br>Also we need to get a meeting time down. I will start a thread
					on the board. Please post if you can come at that time or not, and if not
					what time would be better for you. Late Saturday night is what I'm
					aiming at as most people seem to be avaible then. I will also start
					up a second thread so we can address anything we need to talk about
					during the meeting. I hope to see you all there.
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com">Boisvert</a><br><br>
